<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Signup Complete — sLab Delegates</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; background:#0a0a0a; color:#e5e5e5; min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:24px; }
    .wrap { max-width:480px; width:100%; text-align:center; }
    .logo { font-size:24px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; margin-bottom:24px; } .logo span { color:#c9a848; }
    .card { background:#141414; border:1px solid #262626; border-radius:8px; padding:40px 32px; }
    .icon { font-size:48px; margin-bottom:16px; }
    h1 { font-size:20px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px; }
    p { font-size:14px; color:#a3a3a3; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:16px; }
    .highlight { color:#c9a848; font-weight:500; }
    .btn { display:inline-block; padding:10px 24px; background:#c9a848; color:#0a0a0a; border-radius:4px; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; transition:background 0.15s; margin-top:8px; }
    .btn:hover { background:#d4b85c; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="logo"><span>s</span>Lab</div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">&#9989;</div>
      <h1>Welcome, <%= name %>!</h1>
      <p>Your delegate account has been created. Your application is <span class="highlight">pending review</span> by our team.</p>
      <p>Once approved, you'll receive access to your delegate panel where you can track commissions, view assigned accounts, and manage your profile.</p>
      <p>In the meantime, make sure your contact and tax information is up to date — you'll need valid tax info on file before your first payout.</p>
      <a href="/delegates/login" class="btn">Go to Login</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
